text: Randonauting is an interesting activity, check my reply under Hakan's original tweet for some general thoughts. Curious how we make our little tunnels through reality and become blind to everything outside of them. Another thing here is the cosmic law of manifestation/attraction

This can also be done without the coordinate app, just visualizing/contemplating something and going for a walk leading to it, but this way the process is easier as the habitual factor is removed... The relation between thought and object goes both ways I believe, not only...

Do you manifest the object from your thoughts into the future, but the object manifests itself in your thoughts, this is why it would be hard to use this method for some sort of worldly gain. Overall fascinating phenomenon, but one we need to be careful with
